Sailthru::Client
===========

DOCUMENTATION

http://getstarted.sailthru.com/developers/api-libraries/perl

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

Make sure to strip all newlines (whether literal or "\n" encoded from request
parameters) or JSON encoding will fail.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Module (latest tested version)
------
Encode (2.47)
Digest::MD5 (2.52)
HTTP::Request (6.00)
JSON::XS (2.33)
LWP (6.04)
LWP::Protocol::https (6.04)
Params::Validate (1.06)
URI::Escape (3.31)

